  "method": [
    "In a bowl, mix all the ingredients for the tikki, except the oil. Mash well and roll the mixture into palm-sized tikkis.",
    "In a pan, heat the oil and shallow fry the tikkis until golden.",
    "To make the chaat, place the hot tikkis on a plate. Top them with the yoghurt, sprouts, the chutneys, a pinch of chaat masala, red chilli powder, cumin powder, coriander leaves and sev. Serve fresh."
